# Azure AI Language Text Summarizer - REST API Examples
# Comprehensive collection of HTTP requests for text summarization

# ============================================================================
# SETUP AND CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================

# Set your Azure AI Language service endpoint and API key
@endpoint = {{AZURE_LANGUAGE_ENDPOINT}}
@api_key = {{AZURE_LANGUAGE_KEY}}
@api_version = 2023-04-01

# Common headers
@content_type = application/json
@subscription_key = Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key

# ============================================================================
# 1. EXTRACTIVE SUMMARIZATION
# ============================================================================

### 1.1 Basic Extractive Summarization
POST {{endpoint}}/language/analyze-text/jobs?api-version={{api_version}}
{{subscription_key}}: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
    "displayName": "ExtractiveTextSummarization",
    "analysisInput": {
        "documents": [
            {
                "id": "1",
                "language": "en",
                "text": "The COVID-19 pandemic has fundamentally changed how we work, learn, and interact with each other. Remote work has become the norm for many organizations, leading to increased adoption of digital collaboration tools and cloud-based services. Educational institutions have shifted to online learning platforms, while healthcare systems have embraced telemedicine to provide safe patient care. The pandemic has also accelerated digital transformation across industries, with businesses investing heavily in automation and artificial intelligence to maintain operations during lockdowns. However, these changes have also highlighted the digital divide, as not everyone has equal access to technology and high-speed internet. As we move forward, it's clear that the lessons learned during the pandemic will continue to shape our future, with hybrid work models, digital-first approaches, and increased focus on resilience becoming permanent features of our society."
            }
        ]
    },
    "tasks": [
        {
            "kind": "ExtractiveSummarization",
            "taskName": "ExtractiveSummarizationTask",
            "parameters": {
                "sentenceCount": 3,
                "sortBy": "Rank"
            }
        }
    ]
}

